ROW.title: PLUS Version
ROW.tagdesc: The version number of the PLUS standards in place at the time of the transaction.

ROW.title: Licensee
ROW.tagdesc: Party or parties to whom the license is granted by the Licensor/s under the license transaction.

ROW.title: Licensee ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying each Licensee.

ROW.title: Licensee Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of each Licensee.

ROW.title: End User
ROW.tagdesc: Party or parties ultimately making use of the image under the license.

ROW.title: End User ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying each End User.

ROW.title: End User Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of each End User.

ROW.title: Licensor
ROW.tagdesc: Party or parties granting the license to the Licensee.

ROW.title: Licensor ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying each Licensor.

ROW.title: Licensor Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of each Licensor.

ROW.title: Licensor Address
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor street address.

ROW.title: Licensor Address Detail
ROW.tagdesc: Additional Licensor mailing address details.

ROW.title: Licensor City
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor City name.

ROW.title: Licensor State or Province
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor State or Province name.

ROW.title: Licensor Postal Code
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Postal Code or Zip Code.

ROW.title: Licensor Country
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Country name.

ROW.title: Licensor Telephone Type 1
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Telephone Type 1.

ROW.title: Licensor Telephone 1
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Telephone number 1.

ROW.title: Licensor Telephone Type 2
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Telephone Type 2.

ROW.title: Licensor Telephone 2
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Telephone number 2.

ROW.title: Licensor Email
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor Email address.

ROW.title: Licensor URL
ROW.tagdesc: Licensor world wide web address.

ROW.title: Licensor Notes
ROW.tagdesc: Supplemental information for use in identifying and contacting the Licensor/s.

ROW.title: PLUS Media Summary Code
ROW.tagdesc: A PLUS-standardized alphanumeric code string summarizing the media usages included in the license.

ROW.title: License Start Date
ROW.tagdesc: The date on which the license takes effect.

ROW.title: License End Date
ROW.tagdesc: The date on which the license expires.

ROW.title: Media Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints limiting the scope of PLUS Media Usage/s included in the license to particular named media or to media not yet specifically defined in the PLUS Media Matrix.

ROW.title: Region Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints limiting the scope of geographic distribution to specific cities, states, provinces or other areas to be included in or excluded from the PLUS Regions specified in the Media Usages specified in the license.

ROW.title: Product or Service Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints limiting usage of the image to promotion of/association with a named product or service.

ROW.title: Image File Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints on the changing of the image file name, metadata or file type.

ROW.title: Image Alteration Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints on alteration of the image by cropping, flipping, retouching, colorization, de-colorization or merging.

ROW.title: Image Duplication Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Constraints on the creation of duplicates of the image.

ROW.title: Model Release Status
ROW.tagdesc: Summarizes the availability and scope of model releases authorizing usage of the likenesses of persons appearing in the photograph.

ROW.title: Model Release ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier associated with each Model Release.

ROW.title: Minor Model Age Disclosure
ROW.tagdesc: Age of the youngest model pictured in the image, at the time that the image was made.

ROW.title: Property Release Status
ROW.tagdesc: Summarizes the availability and scope of property releases authorizing usage of the properties appearing in the photograph.

ROW.title: Property Release ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier associated with each Property Release.

ROW.title: Other Constraints
ROW.tagdesc: Additional constraints on the license.

ROW.title: Credit Line Required
ROW.tagdesc: Attribution requirements, if any.

ROW.title: Adult Content Warning
ROW.tagdesc: Warning indicating the presence of content not suitable for minors.

ROW.title: Other License Requirements
ROW.tagdesc: Additional license requirements.

ROW.title: Terms and Conditions Text
ROW.tagdesc: Terms and Conditions applying to the license.

ROW.title: Terms and Conditions URL
ROW.tagdesc: URL for Terms and Conditions applying to the license.

ROW.title: Other License Conditions
ROW.tagdesc: Additional license conditions.

ROW.title: Image Type
ROW.tagdesc: Identifies the type of image delivered.

ROW.title: Licensor Image ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier assigned by the Licensor to the image.

ROW.title: Image File Name As Delivered
ROW.tagdesc: Name of the image file delivered to the Licensee for use under the license.

ROW.title: Image File Format As Delivered
ROW.tagdesc: File format of the image file delivered to the Licensee for use under the license.

ROW.title: Image File Size As Delivered
ROW.tagdesc: Size of the image file delivered to the Licensee.

ROW.title: Copyright Status
ROW.tagdesc: Copyright status of the image.

ROW.title: Copyright Registration Number
ROW.tagdesc: Copyright Registration Number, if any, applying to the licensed image.

ROW.title: First Publication Date
ROW.tagdesc: The date on which the image was first published.

ROW.title: Copyright Owner
ROW.tagdesc: Owner or owners of the copyright in the licensed image.

ROW.title: Copyright Owner ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying each Copyright Owner.

ROW.title: Copyright Owner Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of Copyright Owner.

ROW.title: Copyright Owner Image ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier assigned by the Copyright Owner to the image.

ROW.title: Image Creator
ROW.tagdesc: Creator/s of the image.

ROW.title: Image Creator ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying each Image Creator.

ROW.title: Image Creator Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of Image Creator.

ROW.title: Image Creator Image ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier assigned by the Image Creator to the image.

ROW.title: Image Supplier ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID identifying the Image Supplier.

ROW.title: Image Supplier Name
ROW.tagdesc: Name of Image Supplier.

ROW.title: Image Supplier Image ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier assigned by the Image Supplier to the image.

ROW.title: Licensee Image ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional identifier assigned by the Licensee to the image.

ROW.title: Licensee Image Notes
ROW.tagdesc: Notes added by Licensee.

ROW.title: Other Image Info
ROW.tagdesc: Additional image information.

ROW.title: License ID
ROW.tagdesc: Optional PLUS-ID assigned by the Licensor to the License.

ROW.title: Licensor Transaction ID
ROW.tagdesc: Identifier assigned by Licensor for Licensor's reference and internal use.

ROW.title: Licensee Transaction ID
ROW.tagdesc: Identifier assigned by Licensee for Licensee's reference and internal use.

ROW.title: Licensee Project Reference
ROW.tagdesc: Project reference name or description assigned by Licensee.

ROW.title: License Transaction Date
ROW.tagdesc: The date of the License Transaction.

ROW.title: Reuse
ROW.tagdesc: Indicates whether a license is a repeat or an initial license. Reuse may require that licenses stored in files previously delivered to the customer be updated.

ROW.title: Other License Documents
ROW.tagdesc: Reference information for additional documents associated with the license.

ROW.title: Other License Info
ROW.tagdesc: Additional license information.

ROW.title: Custom 1
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensor's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 2
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensor's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 3
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensor's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 4
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensor's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 5
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensor's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 6
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensee's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 7
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensee's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 8
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensee's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 9
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensee's discretion.

ROW.title: Custom 10
ROW.tagdesc: Optional field for use at Licensee's discretion.
